title: [Shattered Moors]
description: Mist obscures the moors beyond the trail, turning the landscape into an eldritch patchwork of greens and browns.  The mist seems to catch the moonlight, which gives it an otherworldly glow.  A few wild roses, little more than pale splashes of pink, grow among the heather and gorse.
